def my_func(input1: str):
    if not (1 <= len(input1) <= 20) or not all(c in 'tf|&' for c in input1):
        return False

    tokens = list(input1)
    while '|' in tokens or '&' in tokens:
        i = 0
        while i < len(tokens):
            if tokens[i] == '&':
                left = tokens[i - 1] == 't'
                right = tokens[i + 1] == 't'
                tokens[i - 1:i + 2] = ['t' if left and right else 'f']
                i -= 1
            i += 1

        i = 0
        while i < len(tokens):
            if tokens[i] == '|':
                left = tokens[i - 1] == 't'
                right = tokens[i + 1] == 't'
                tokens[i - 1:i + 2] = ['t' if left or right else 'f']
                i -= 1
            i += 1

    return tokens[0] == 't'
